dc_description_s: 1965 edition.; Distributed by Shell Oil Company.; Includes index to counties, cities and towns.; Public recreational areas chart, Indiana mileage chart and ancillary maps of Chicago and vicinity; South Bend, Indiana; Fort Wayne, Indiana; Indianapolis, Indiana; Terre Haute, Indiana; Evansville, Indiana and Transcontinental road map on verso. Scale 1:760,000. 1 inch = approximately 12 miles.
